    {
      "id": "518d8607-8ac1-42ae-aae5-909752ad3ecd",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -800,
        -304
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 528,
        "height": 528,
        "content": "# 📰 AI-Powered RSS Feed Tracker & Notifier\n\n**Objective:** Automatically monitor an RSS feed, use AI to extract key information into structured data, log it, and trigger email alerts.\n\n**How it works:**\n1. **Trigger:** Checks the RSS feed for new content on a set schedule.\n2. **AI Processing:** AI Agent extracts Title, Date/Time, URL, and Description into clean JSON format.\n3. **Storage & Alert:** Logs the structured data into a spreadsheet and sends an email notification to the team.\n\n**Setup Requirements:**\n- Target RSS Feed URL.\n- OpenAI (or equivalent) API Credentials.\n- Google Sheets & Microsoft Outlook OAuth connections."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "67ca2d0b-3952-41dd-9d7f-760baefb8e76",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -192,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 384,
        "height": 480,
        "content": "## Phase 1 — Ingestion & AI Extraction\nFetches feed items, processes them one by one, and uses an AI model to extract specific data points.\n\n**Node Flow:**\n1. **RSS Feed Trigger:** Polls the target feed for new updates.\n2. **Loop Over Items:** Processes one RSS item at a time to prevent data overlap.\n3. **AI Agent (with LLM):** Reads raw text and structures it (title, date, url, description).\n4. **Code in JavaScript:** Sanitizes the AI output (strips markdown blocks) and parses the JSON object."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e5abb1d3-409d-489f-866d-df79688f6ccc",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        320,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 512,
        "height": 400,
        "content": "## Phase 2 — Logging & Notifications\nTakes the parsed AI data, saves it to a database/spreadsheet, and notifies stakeholders.\n\n**Node Flow:**\n1. **Google Sheets:** Maps the parsed JSON keys and appends a new row to the tracking sheet.\n2. **Send a message (Outlook):** Dispatches an automated email alert containing the update details.\n3. **Loop Return:** Connects back to the \"Loop Over Items\" node to process the next item in the batch."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    }
